instructions: At the double lane intersection ahead, turn right and cross it fully. Pass by Starbucks on the right. Go to the next light with Happy Socks on the right, turn left. At the next light with Cole Haan on the right corner turn right. Go about 3/4 down the block. Stop when you reach Canada Goose Flagship on right. Chanel, too far.

Go through the first lights. Go to the end of the long block and turn right at the lights. Pass Chanel and Diesel on the left and turn left at the first set of lights. Stop just before reaching a gap between buildings on the left. BAPE store should be ahead on the left. You are stopping near the end of the first building.

Pass a bike rental on the right and turn right at the light. Turn left at the light with Duane Reade on the far right corner. Go through the next light and stop almost all the way at the end of the block, next to BBar & Grill on the right and Crunch on the left.

Go to the third traffic light and turn right. Pass through another light immediately after and continue towards the next intersection, passing Saint Patrick's Old Cathedral on the right. Stop before the intersection in the middle of the green space area before the light.

Turn right at the light in front of you. Pass Uncle Ted's and turn left at the next light. Go down the block and straight through the first light. At the light immediately after, turn right and there will be a parking area on the left. Go through the next light and stop in front of the playground, just before the curve.

Start straight, you'll be at a double light intersection. Turn left at the 2nd light in that intersection and go straight to the next light. Turn right and pass the 1st left side street and turn left at the 2nd side street. Go down until another double light intersection and stop in the middle of that intersection.

Go straight to the first light and turn left. Follow this road for a few blocks, passing The Noho Star and Gato on your right before coming to a major intersection with a divided road. Cross the divided road and stop shortly after, there will be an REI on your left.

Head down the block and pass through the light. At the next light you will make a right. You will pass a bus stop on the left and stop just before getting to the next light with Mercer Street Residence Hall on your left.

Pass the Market NYC on the left and go through the lights. Turn left at the following lights. Go through the intersection after Benetton on the right and go through the following lights. Pass the parking area on the right and stop as Ladder 20 / Division 1 on left ends. You will be at a space between buildings on the right.

Head to the lights with Wholefoods on the left corner. Cross the street to the other side, then turn right immediately. Go past the next 3 lights with The Market NYC on the left corner. At the 4th light with REI on the near left corner, turn left, take one step forward, then stop.

At the corner with Chanel on the right, make a right turn. Proceed to the next light and make a left turn. Go straight to the next light with the Apple Store SoHo on the right corner. Make a right turn here. Proceed past the next light with Fanelli Cafe. Go to the end of the block and stop next to Victoria Secret on right.
Head to the first light and make a right. Continue through the next two lights and pass the Half Pint on the right corner. At the next light turn right and then stop a few paces after turning.

Pass The Bowery Hotel on the left and turn right at the lights. Turn right at the next set of lights and then take the left side street and go through the double intersection. Take two steps and stop at the first building.

Go straight to first intersection and make a left at corner with Armani Exchange. Go straight through first two intersections. Destination is in the third intersection with Miss Paradis to left and St. Patrick's Cathedral across the street to left.
Head straight to the 2nd light just past Antique Garage on the right and turn right. At the next light with Boffi and bike rentals on the far left corner, turn left and stop.

Turn left at the stoplight ahead of you, with Starbucks on the corner. There are two lights very close together here, be sure to take the first. Go straight through three more lights, passing a church and a parking lot on the way. Stop just after the street begins to bend. You will have just passed a park on the left.

Head straight past the T-intersection. At the next light with Ben's Pizza on your left, turn right. Go past the next 2 lights. There should be a church on your left corner. At the 3rd light, turn right and stop. There should be bike rentals on your right up ahead.

Head straight past 2 intersections. At the 3rd intersection with The Red Lion on your far right corner, turn right. At the next light with Arturo's Pizza on your near left corner, turn left. Stop at the next intersection. You should see Starbucks on your near right corner and Silver Spurs on your near left corner.

Go straight through three intersections. At the fourth intersection make a left into the far right lane of traffic after the median. Proceed straight until you are able to turn right. Destination is shortly after the turn and several steps before you get to Morgenstern's Finest Ice Cream.

Go straight until you reach a bus stop on your left. Then turn left. Turn right at Bar Veloce on the next block. Go straight through the immediate light. Pass Cooke Center Academy on the left before a right side street. Keep going until you pass Rouge et Blanc on the left, then stop.

Head down the block and at the first light with Silver Spurs on the corner make a right. Head through the next two lights, passing a bakery on the right and stop just past Miss Lily's restaurant on the right just after that light.

Go to the light and make a left passing Noho Star on the right corner. Head to the third light and make a right. Stop just before Merchant's House Museum on the left. It's a little more than 1/4 of the way down.

Go straight until you come to the first set of lights. Go through these lights. At the following set of lights, turn left. The Red Lion is on the right corner. Go about half way down the block. Looks for Tomoe Sushi and Lupa on the left hand side. You want to stop about 2 buildings before Tomoe Sushi.

Head straight to the light and make a left. You will then go past all the different retailers and pass through another two lights. At the third light with Solstice on the corner you will make a left and stop after a couple of paces.

Go straight until you have passed two bus stops on the right. Then pass Chipotle on the right and turn right. Pass another bus stop and stop in front of the doctor's office on the right. It's before Angelika Film Center on the right and a light.

Go straight until you reach the end of the street and turn right. When you reach the light, turn left. There will be a university building on your left and Think Coffee on the right. Turn right when you are able. Stop halfway down the block, just as you reach Duane Reade.

Go to the lights and turn left. At the next corner, before the lights, turn right. Follow this street until a left hand turn is available. 12 Chairs and Comodo will be on the right. Turn left and stop 1 step after turning.

Go to the traffic light where KITH NYC clothing store is on the far left corner. Turn right. Go down the long block passing Chipotle on the right and Urban Outfitters on the left. At the traffic light, Crate and Barrel is on the right. Go thru on light and the next light immediately after and stop with Hollister on the left.

Go to the lights and turn right. Go to the second set of lights and turn right. Astor Wines & Spirits will be on the left. Go almost to the end of this block. Stop when 2 Cooper is on your left and just before BBar & Grill on the right.

Walk to the light and turn right. At the next light with Fanelli Cafe on the far right corner, turn left. Go past the next light with Prada on your left corner. Stop at the next intersection with Juice Generation on your far left corner and Duane Reade on your right.

Walk straight passing a church on the right to the light. Turn right and go to the next light. Turn left there and at the next light, Happy Socks may be on the right corner. Turn right here. Stop more than 1/2 down the block possibly next to DKNY on the right side and some bike rental racks on the left side.

Go to the end of the block passing Happy Socks on the left corner and turn left at the lights. Go to the second set of lights. The Dutch is on the right corner and you will turn right here. Take 2 steps and stop. Do not go as far as Once Upon a Tart.

Head all the way down to the light passing Cookie Dough on the left and make a left at the light. Pass by Half Pint on the left and through the light. Go past the next light and stop in front of the building on the left.
Head past the market and the cathedral and make a right at the light. At the next light with the Delicatessen on the corner make a left. Stop in front of the fire hall.

Turn right at the second light, then go through another one immediately. Pass two churches connected to cemeteries on the same block and cross the street. Stop in front of Chrome on the left. If you reach Spacecowboys, you need to go back a bit.
Go to the light and turn left. You will pass SoHo Cafe on the way to a light. When you reach it, turn right. Stop at the next light. There should be a Lure Fishbar on the far right corner.

Go straight through the first intersection and at second intersection make a right. Baseball field will be to your left after you turn. Go straight through first intersection and stop in the middle of next intersection. This is destination just after Minetta Tavern Restaurant to left and MacDougal Street Ale House to right.

Turn left at the light right in front of you. Pass 2 intersections that are just side streets. The third intersection might have The Bowery Hotel far left corner, head straight to the next light. Go straight and stop a few stops after this light just passed the building after The Bowery Market, about 3 buildings in.

Go to the corner and turn right. Pass Chipotle on the right before coming to a double light intersection, Crate and Barrel on the corner. Go through both lights. Pass Bank of America on the right before coming to a light. Turn right, take a step and stop. Prada should just be starting on your right, Victoria Secret on left.

Go to the intersection, turn left at the first set of double lights. Starbucks is on the left. Turn right at the next light, go straight through the next immediate light where Arturo's Pizza is. At the next light turn left. Stop at the 3rd building on the right. If you get to Uncle Ted's it's too far.

Walk past 3 left side streets until you reach a 4-way intersection with The Noho Star possibly on the far left corner. Turn left here and go forward passing Temple Bar and Gato to the double light intersection. Stop in the middle of the second light, with a REI on the far left corner.

Go to the light and turn left. At the following light, turn right. You'll pass a large parking area on the left. You will then come to a double intersection. Go through the first light of it and turn left at the second one of it immediately after. Stop just before coming to the following light, just past Phebes on the right.

Walk past the sports courts on the left to the light and turn right. Head to the end of the road which is intersected by a double light intersection. Turn left at the 2nd one. Pass a T-intersection stop 1/2 to the next light, just after a bus stop and next to The Bowery House, both on the right.

Go to the lights and turn left. Follow this street along and you will come to an intersection with 2 sets of lights very close together. Go through both these lights. REI will be on the left. At the end of this block you will turn right. Benetton is the store on your right and you will stop at it.

Go straight to the light with the park ahead of you and turn left. With the park now on your right side, go through the following light with bike rentals on the right corner. Go almost to the end of the next block and stop 2 steps before the next light. Whole Foods Bowery Beer Room will be on your left.

Head to the light and turn right at the first light at that intersection. Go straight through 2 lights, you may see Happy Paws. On the third block at the light turn left. Go straight until you reach the side street and stop, this might be immediately after Puck Fair.

Turn right at the traffic light. You're going to pass through 2 traffic lights which are very close together and then go down a whole block. At the end of the block turn left. Your destination is in the middle of the next intersection. There is a by Chloe restaurant on the corner.

Walk past a NYU building to the intersection and turn left. Walk past a bike rental to the end of the road and turn right. Turn left at the next light with Duane Reade on the corner. Go to the next light with La Colombe and Astor Wines on the corners. Cross it and stop a step or 2 after crossing next to Astor Wines.

Head to the light with the Angelika Film Center on the right corner, then turn right. Go past the next 2 traffic lights. At the 3rd traffic light with REI on the far right corner, cross the street, then come to a stop.

Go past the 1st light with Soho Cafe at the far right corner. At the 2nd light, turn left. At the next light just past Antique Garage on your right, turn right. Continue to the next light with Boffi on your far left corner. Cross the street and stop between the 2nd and 3rd building on your left.

Walk to the first intersection with Juice Generation on the corner and turn left. At the next light, turn right. Pass a small parking lot and fire station on the way to the next light which has two straight forks bordering a park. Take the left path, pass the park and stop in the middle of the light near La Esquina.

Head straight through the intersection close to you. Go straight through the next light. At the third light you will take a right. Stop just before the next light, you might pass a grocery shop on you way.
Turn right at the corner. Turn left at SoHo Cafe on the left. Pass Chase on the left and cross the street. Stop in front of Uniqlo SOHO on the right. If you reach H&M, you've gone too far.

Follow the road as it curves. When you come to the light, it's a double. Turn right at the first one. The following light will have Crunch on the corner, turn right. Go through the following light, Astor Wines on the corner. Pass Blink Fitness Noho on the left, and when you come to the light, stop in the intersection.

Head to the intersection and make a left turn. Go straight to the 3rd intersection where you will see The Dutch on your right. Make a left turn. Your destination is between the 2nd and 3rd building on your left, right before the Blue Ribbon.

Go to the light with Chanel on the corner and turn right. Walk the block passing Diesel to the next light and turn left. Walk the long block past a BAPE Store. At the light there should be an Apple Store on the right corner. Stop in the middle of the intersection.

Turn right at Crunch a couple of blocks ahead. Pass Merchant's House Museum and then turn left at Astor Wines & Spirits on the right. Go past Screaming Mimi's on the right before turning right. Stop at the bike rental on the right.

Go to the first set of light. Think Coffee will be on the left corner. Turn right here. At the following set of lights, turn left and cross through the next set of lights that are immediately after. Follow the block along to the lights at the end of the street and stop at lights. Blue Ribbon Fried Chicken will be on the left.

Head to the corner and make a left with Lure Fishbar on the corner. You will then head through two more lights, passing a Starbucks on your right after the second light. At the following light make a right and stop in front of the Duane Reade on the corner.

Turn right at the second light. When you reach Chef Restaurant Supplies on the left, turn left. If you reach a garden on the left, go back a street. Stop just before 310 Bowery Bar on the left, which is at the top of a T-intersection.
Go straight and take a right at the next light. Go straight through the next 2 lights and at the following light take a left and stop immediately after turning.

You will start near Public Theater, and continue down this road until you reach Blink Fitness Noho, where you will make a left. Continue down this road past the bank and past Crunch, where you will make a right when you see Phebes.
Turn right at the lights. Go the third set of lights and turn right. After a few steps stop just after Saint Laurent Paris on the left. If you reach Patagonia you went too far.

Go past three green spaces on the left and two on the right. When you pass a bus stop in front of a ball field, turn left. Stop when you are between third base and home at the ball field. If you reach a light, you've gone too far.

Head straight passing a playground on a left to a 6-way intersection. Starting from the right, take the 2nd street and go straight through 1 4-way intersection, 1 traffic light and at the following light, there should be Le Poisson Rouge and the Red Lion on the corners. Stop in the middle of this intersection.

Go through the intersection ahead, Cole Haan on the far corner. At the following light, Happy Socks on the corner, turn left. Pass DKNY on the right, and when you get to the light, turn right. Pass Arc'teryx Soho on the right, and stop at the end of Boqueria next door, just a step over midway down the block.

Turn left at the corner. Go straight until you can't anymore, then turn right. Pass the International Center of Photography Museum on the left. Then pass Rainbow Kitchen Hardware Supplies on the left and turn left. Take one or two steps, then stop.

Go through the light ahead. The following light has a playground on the right, go through it. There is a double intersection soon after, go through both lights. You'll pass a ballfield on the right. Take a left at the light, but not the sharpest left. Pass a park on right, turn left at light. Stop in front of church on right.

Go straight through the traffic light ahead. At the next traffic light you're going to turn left. Go straight through the next intersection and then right at the traffic light. Mark this as your destination.
Go straight until you have passed Fanelli Cafe and Cole Haan on the left, then turn right. Stop just before Soho Wines & Spirits on the right.
Go to the lights and turn right. Continue on through the next 4 sets of lights. Take several steps. Chase will be on the left and Niketown on the right. This is where you want to stop.
Go to the 1st light and turn left. Head straight to the 3rd intersection with the Evolution Store and Le Basket at the corners.

Proceed past the first light with the Apple Store. Turn left at the second light with Longchamp on the right. Continue past the next light with the Google store on the right corner. Go to the end of the next block, stopping one step before the light. Chase Bank should be on your right hand side.

Turn right at the first set of lights. Pass Think Coffee on the left and go through the lights. Pass Noho Star and go through another set of lights. Pass Chef Restaurant Supplies and go through the double lights. go about 1/4 of the way down the block and stop just past Delancey Restaurant Equipment Supply on the left.

Head to the light, Nespresso might be on the near right corner, turn right. Go to the next block and turn left at the Prada Store. Drive all the way down that block and turn right. Stop just after Hollister on your right, just a few paces after turning.

Go to the light and take a left with Starbucks on the corner. Pass the library to the next light and take a left. You will pass LIDS before reaching the next light where you will turn right. Continue to the next intersection while Tisch school is on your left. Take a left and stop three fourths down.

Go straight and take a right at the first intersection where Google store is. Continue through the next two intersections and at the third one, take a right where you see Duane Reade. Stop just past the bike rental.

Walk to the light and turn left. Pass the Dutch and cross the street. The next intersection has a tiny park on the left corner. Walk to the far corner of the park and turn right at that light. Go through a light and at the forking road, take the left one so you are on the right of a fire station. Stop 1 step before the light.

Pass through the intersection with Cole Haan on the corner. When you come to the following light with the Apple Store on the far corner, turn right. Continue down the long block, passing BAPE on the right. When you come to the light, go through it. Go about 1/3 down the block, and stop in front of Versus Versace on the right.

Go straight through the intersection ahead. Take a right turn just past Comedy Cellar. Go straight. Ignore a left turn. At the next crossing with Minetta Playground, don't turn left but go through ahead and to the left. Take a right at Our Lady of Pompeii Church crossing. Stop just before the next crossing just past Pasticceria.

Head to the first light and make a right. Go all the way down the block and you will pass through another light. Towards the end of the next block there will be a park on your right. Make a left at the light and head down until you reach Arc'teryx Soho store on left right before the light and stop.

At the first intersection make a right and at the next intersection make a left with Duane Reade on the corner. Go through the next light and head to the following light and you will stop there. There will be a Crunch fitness on the corner.

You will start near Da Silvano. You will continue down this street until you reach Winston Churchill Square, where you will make the second left at this intersection. You will pass by Trattoria Spaghetto and Starbucks. You will make a left on the street past the Starbucks where you will reach the destination.

Walk by Happy Socks to the light and turn right. Walk through the next 3 intersection, the 2nd has an Apple Store and the 3rd has The Mercer Kitchen on the corner. Stop a few steps before the next light before some subway entrances. Pink and Prada should be on either side of you.

Head to the intersection with The Red Lion and make a right. At the next intersection, make a left. Continue to the next intersection where you will see a post box. Make a right. Go forward two steps and stop in front of Miss Lily's on your right.

Walk down to the light and make the immediate left. Go through two lights. On the third block, you'll see a bus stop on the left. Make a right and the following light. Go across one immediate light, then down toward the end of the block. Go past the church on the right. Stop before the bike rental on the right.

Go straight to the intersection and make a right. Go straight through one intersection without a light and then go through the next intersection with a light. Pass The Bitter end on left and at the following light with The Red Lion on the corner turn left. Stop a couple steps before the first light with Arturo's Pizza on left.

Head to the first light and make a right. You will then go to the next light and make a left with a Chase on the far left corner. Go all the way through the next light passing Soho Cafe on the previous corner. Stop just before getting to the Starbucks on your right and just past Topman.

Go through the first two sets of lights. You will pass Adidas and Crate and Barrel on the right. At the next set of lights turn right. Angelika Film Center is on right corner. Go towards the end of the Rec Center on your left. Stop before reaching the bike rental on left.

Go through the first intersection and turn at the second. Apartment buildings will be on your left. Pass through the first set of lights. A recreation Center is on your left. Turn at the light after that. Pass Angelika Film Center on right and head to bike rental near end of block. Stop just before bike rental.

Turn right at the light ahead. Keep the park on your left as you turn left at the next light. Go straight through a T-intersection and turn right at the next light, leaving the park behind. Stop a step before the end of the first building on the right. If you reach a coffee shop on the left, you've gone too far.

Go straight through the first light. At the second light make a left turn. At the first intersection make a right turn and just cross over the median to the far lanes of traffic. This is the destination.

Make a left at the light and pass Prada, Under Armour, and Bank of America on the left. Make a right at the light. Go through the next two lights and stop two steps after the last one you go through. REI should be to your right.

Head straight to the next intersection with bike rentals to your right corner, then make a left turn. At the following intersection with Atrium on the left corner, make a right turn. Walk to the next set of lights with Adidas on the left corner. Cross the street, then stop.

Go to the second set of lights and turn left. Crunch should be on the right corner. Go to the second set of lights. Duane Reade should be on the left corner. Stop immediately after the lights. You will still be in the intersection.

Pass a right side street and turn left at the first set of lights at the double light intersection. Pass a small garden on your left and go through both sets of lights in the double intersection. Pass Whole Foods on the left and turn right at the next corner. Cross to the other side of the street and stop.

Turn right at the corner ahead. Pass a playground on the left, then Duane Reade on the left. Go through this intersection, which has subway entrances on each corner. Turn right when you reach Starbucks on the left. Take a few steps and stop.

Pass a garden on the left as you head to the lights where you will turn right. Pass another garden on the left corner and turn left. Pass a parking area on the left and turn right at the lights. Turn right at the next set of lights. Stop as the green space on the left starts. Eileen's Cheesecake is on the right.

With a church and square on the corners, go through a light. At the next light, go straight so you are on the right of a playground. Walk to the end of the street and turn left. Pass Comedy Cellar to the next light and turn right. Pass a residence hall to the light and turn right. Stop 1/3 down the block, next to Sacred Chow.

Walk forward to the double light intersection and turn right at the 1st one. At the next light with a ball field on the far right corner, turn left. Go through the entire intersection and turn right at the side street. At the light with Charley Bird, turn left. Stop 1/2 down the block, just before a bus stop on the left.

Turn right at the first set of lights with Fanelli Cafe on the corner. Go through the next set of lights after Apple Store on the right. Pass the next intersection with Cole Haan on the left and then turn right at the following lights. Pass Soho Wines & Spirits on the right and stop 2 buildings after that.

Go straight through 2 of the next traffic lights. The 3rd intersection should be very large. Turn right on the road going against traffic and go straight through 2 more traffic lights. Just before the 3rd light, stop. You should see an REI on the far left corner across the intersection.

Head straight to the light with the playground on your right and turn left. Go through the next 3 lights with Longchamp on the right corner. When you get to the 4th light with Google Store on the right corner, cross the street.

Walk down to the intersection and turn left. Walk past a T-intersection. At the next intersection it will again be straight or right turn. Take the right turn and walk down the block. There will be two sets of lights to go over then another block. You'll pass a church on the right. Stop just past the bike rental on the left.

Go forward and turn right at the first intersection. Take a left at the next light. Go down to the end of the block where there is a large intersection with Starbucks on the other side. Turn left and stop after a couple steps, in front of a bus stop.

Go straight to the light, passing St. Anthony of Padua Church. At the second light immediately after the first, take a left. Continue to the next light and turn right. You will pass by MacDougal-Sullivan Gardens Historic District, and stop in the middle of the next intersection.

Go straight to the light and turn left. Go straight through the first two lights, and at the third light with Taim on the far left corner, turn left. Stop about halfway to the first intersection, past Spacecowboys on right, before Rubirosa on left and right next to Chrome on your right.

With a church on your right, walk to the T-intersection and turn right. You'll pass a church on either side as you go through the next light. At the following light with Le Poisson Rouge and The Red Lion on the corners, turn left. Walk to the next light and turn right. Walk and stop in the middle of the garden on the left.

Go through the first set of lights and then turn left at the ones immediately after. Pass Crunch on the right corner and go through the lights. Continue through the next two sets of lights pass Bowery Market and Bowery Hotel on the right corners. Stop at the next set of lights with Think Coffee on the corner.

Go straight through the next light and at the second one take a left through the double lights which should be right after the bar on the right. Go through the next intersection and light past the liquor store on the right. At the next light stop under it in the intersection where Duane Reade is on the corner.

Walk down to the corner and turn left. Walk past a bus stop on the right. You'll go through on light. At the second light, you'll turn right. Walk past the bike rental on the left. At the corner, turn left. Take an immediate right and stop a few steps past the corner.

Turn left at the second light. Go straight until you pass a ballfield on your right. Go through the intersection at the end of it and see green space on your left. Stop just after it begins. There will be a mailbox on your right.

Head to the first light and make a right. Pass Loreley Gardens on the right and at the next light make a left. A large park will be on your right and you will go through the next light. Head about half way up the block, just past the refreshments at the park on right and stop.

Go to the end of the block and turn right at the light. At the next intersection turn left, with by Chloe on the near right corner. Go to the end of this long block, passing a ballfield on the right, before going through two lights close together. Stop at the end of the next intersection, next to 12 Chairs on the left.

Turn left at the lights. Hollister is on the left corner. Go to the following lights with Prada on the right and turn left. Pass Dean and Deluca on the right and go through the 4-way intersection and then the lights with G-Star Raw on the corner. Stop between the two buildings on the right, just after a deli.

Head to the light and turn right. At the next light with Happy Socks on the near right corner, turn left. Go down the long block to the next double lights with Starbucks on the near left corner. Cross the street and stop. Silver Spurs should be on the left corner.
Go ahead to the traffic light and turn right. Go straight through the traffic light ahead passing a playground on your left. Your destination is in the middle of the upcoming intersection.

Go straight through two lights, passing Le Poisson Rouge on the left just after the first. At the next intersection, with by Chloe on the near right corner, turn left. Go to the end of this long block and turn right at the next light. Pass a park on your right. Take the left fork in the road and stop a couple steps after it.

Head straight to the 3rd traffic light with Phebes on the near right corner and Crunch on the far left corner, then make a left turn. Walk to the next light with Astor Wines & Spirits on the near right corner. Turn right here, then take one step before stopping.

Head all the way up the block and make a left at the light. You will head through the next intersection and at the following light make a hard right. You will have a triangle park on your left and you will stop in the middle of the park.

Head to the first light and at the second light with Chase on the corner, continue through. Go through another light and at the following light make a left. Go past Burton on the right and stop just after Patagonia on the left.

Go straight and take a sharp left turn at the light. You'll be turning onto a smaller road, not the main one. Go straight through 2 intersections and stop at the third. The Red Lion will be on the left corner in front of you.

Walk through one light. At the second light, you'll see a playground on the left. Make a left turn. Walk down one block to the next light. Make a right turn. Walk one block to the next light and make a left turn. Stop several steps into this street.

Go down to the corner and turn left. Go through the first light to the next one. You may see Purl Soho on the right before the corner. Turn right. Go most of the way down this block. Stop just past the green space on the left.

Head to the first light and make a left. At the next intersection make a right. Pass an intersection on your left and head to the double set of lights and stop right under the second light with the double street.

Make a left at the light where there should be a SoHo Cafe on the corner. Turn left at the second light, then a right at the next light. Go through one more light and stop a few steps in, next to where there should be a Sweetgreen restaurant on the right corner.

Take straight and cross the 1st intersection road. Go ahead, and take right at the 3rd intersection road. Go straight, take left at traffic light. Go straight and stop 2 steps before at the intersection road.
Turn left at the end of the block. Go straight for a while until you pass Apple Store, SoHo on the left corner. Stop in the center of the next intersection, with Fanelli Cafe on the right.

Go to the light and turn right. Go through the following light, Arturo's Pizza on the corner. Pass Francois Bakery on the right, and go through the following light. When you reach the light, go through it. Go slightly more than half way down the block and stop right before Starbucks on the right.

Go to the double intersection ahead and turn right after the 1st light. At the next intersection where you can only go left, turn left. Continue to the next intersection and stop. You should see bike rentals ahead on right.

Begin by going straight to the traffic light. Turn left and proceed through 1 traffic light, a 4-way intersection, and another traffic light. At the following light, stop in the middle of the intersection. Fanelli Cafe and The Mercer Kitchen should be on the corners of this intersection.

Go to the intersection ahead, Cole Haan on the far corner, and turn left. At the following light, Apple Store on the far corner, turn right. Continue down the long block, passing BAPE store on the right. When you come to the light, turn left. Take a step and stop. Adidas store is too far.

Go straight to the light and turn left. Go straight to the light and turn right. Go straight to the light and turn left. Stop exactly halfway to the first light. If you reach Vin et Fleur on the right you have gone too far.
Head to the end of the block, you should have passed a bike rental. Turn left. Go straight through 2 stop lights and stop in the middle of the 3rd intersection.

Go to the corner and turn right. Go through the double light intersection and at the end of the street, turn left. On the next corner with Atrium and KITH on the corners, turn right. Stop 1/2 to the next light with Mariatash and CEX on your left. Starbucks is slightly too far.

At the end of the block, turn left at the light. Fanelli Cafe will be on your far right corner. At the next light, with Victoria Secret on your near right corner, turn right. Go to the end of this very long block and stop just before the intersection. Niketown will be on your right.

Go through three lights. You'll pass a playground on the left right before the third light. Go one more light - this will be the 4th since you started. There will be a Duane Reade on the left. Turn right, walk until you see the fire station on the right. Stop just before the station.

Go forward to the double intersection and take a left at the 2nd one. University buildings should be on your right. Go forward to the light with a bus stop. Turn right and continue passing more university buildings on the right to the light and turn left. Stop less than 1/2 to the next light next to the Bitter End.

Go straight through 2 traffic lights and a 4-way intersection. At the following light, there is a Prada and multiple subway entrances on the corners. Turn right and stop about 1/2 to the next light, past the Under Armour store and by the Bank of America, both on the right.

Head straight to the first intersection and make a right. Go through another intersection. At the T-intersection you will make a left. Make another right at the corner and stop in the middle of the block.

Go straight through the first two traffic lights and at the third traffic light make a left turn. Go almost to the end of the block, stopping a couple of steps before the light, right after Antique Garage on your right.

Head to the first intersection and make a left. You will pass through a large intersection and at the next T-intersection you will make a right. Head past the next light with St. Patrick's cathedral on your left. Head half way down the block and stop in front of Rubirosa on your right.

Make a left turn at the light directly in front of you. Go past the next set of double lights with Hollister on the far left corner. Walk down the next long block and turn left at the following light with Prada on the near right corner. Stop just after turning left.

Pass the bike rental on the left and go through the lights. At the next set of lights turn left. Pass Sunrise Mart on the left and stop a step after reaching SoHo Anita Dongre GrassRoot Store on the left. It the last large building on the street.

Pass two left side streets and then turn left at the 4-way intersection. Go through the first set of lights with Happy Paws on the right corner and turn left at the lights immediately after. Pass REI on the right corner and go through the next set of lights and then stop when you are through the intersection.

Head straight to the end of the block, this should be a double intersection. Turn left here. Go straight for one block, passing a bunch of shops. Turn right at the light. Head almost to the end of the block, stop about 4 steps from the end of the block.

Walk to the light and turn right. At the next light with by Chloe on the right corner, turn left. Walk down the block passing Dante and a large ball field before getting to a double light intersection. Cross the entire intersection and stop at the corner building on the other side which may be Harry's Corner Shop.

Go to the next light with Longchamp on the right corner, then turn left. At the next light with Apple Store on the right corner, turn right. Go straight to the 2nd light with Prada on the near left corner. Cross the street, then take a step forward. There should be subway entrances on both sides.
Head through the first light and at the second light you will make a left. Continue to the next intersection and make a quick right and then you will stop before going through the intersection.

Go straight to the end of the road to the T-intersection. Take a left and go through a 4-way intersection and a traffic light. Continue forward and pass the right side street and soon after turn right at the next intersection. The Noho Star or Temple Bar should be on the corner. Take a couple steps and Bite may be on the left.

Turn right when you pass Crate and Barrel on the left. Then take an immediate left. Pass a bus stop on the right and turn right. Turn left at the first side street. Pass Benetton on the left and cross the street. Pass Mulberry Branch on the right and stop at the top of the T-intersection in front of the cemetery.

Go straight to the first light and make a right. Pass St. Anthony of Padua Church on your right. Go straight through two lights and stop a couple of steps before the next intersection. You may see the far end of Pegu Club on your right.

Go down the block and turn right at the next light with a park on the right corner. Go past the next intersection with by Chloe on the right corner. Turn left at the next T-intersection with Minetta Tavern on the near left corner. Take one step forward and stop in front of caffe wha on left.

Turn left at the light and pass both lanes of traffic. Continue to the next traffic light. Proceed to one more traffic light, passing a Playground on your right, and turn left at the corner. Stop after a couple of steps just under halfway to the first light.

Go to the light and turn right. Then turn left at the next light, which has Starbucks across the street from it. Go straight through one more light. Pass the bus stop on the right before stopping in front of Chipotle, also on the right.

Head straight to the 3rd traffic light with Prada on the near left corner, then turn left. Proceed to the next light with Hollister on the right corner. Cross the street, then stop. Adidas should be on the right corner.

Head to the first light and proceed through. At the next light you will make a left. Going down the block you will then make a right at the corner and pass a playground on your left. Soon after the playground you will stop in front of the cafe on the left.
Go straight until you pass REI and two bus stops on the left, then turn left at Hollister. Stop in front of Bank of America on the right. It's right before the Under Armour Store.

At the end of the block with Crate and Barrel on the right corner go through the double lights. At the following lights with Prada on the right turn left. Pass Dean and Deluca on the right and go through the intersection. Juice Generation is on the left corner. Take a few steps and stop as the third building on right starts.

Pass bike rental on the left and turn right at the lights. Go through three intersection and pass Happy Paws on the right corner. Go through the first set of lights and stop at the lights immediately after.

Go to the light and turn left. Walk straight to the 3rd intersection with Prada on the far right corner and subway entrances on all corners, then turn left. Walk 1/2 block past H&M and stop in front of Uniqlo SOHO on your left. It's the 5th storefront from the corner.

Go to the first set of lights with Murray's Cheese on the left corner and turn right. Go through the next set of lights. Pass a garden on your left and then turn right at the lights. Follow this road almost to the lights. Stop just after a bus stop on the left. A ballfield is also on the left.

Head to the set of double lights and go through both of them. You will then see a Whole Foods on the corner. Continue to the next light and make a right. You will have a park down the left hand side. Go about 3/4 of the way down the block and stop by the refreshment stand at park.

At the first set of lights with Bowery Market on the left corner turn right. Go through the next three sets of lights passing The Bowery Hotel and Think Coffee on the right. Go towards the end of the block and stop as you reach Chef Restaurant Supplies which is the last building on the right.

Go through one intersection and pass a ballfield on the right and turn left at the lights. Go through another set of lights and continue past Francois bakery on the left. Stop at the last building before the lights.

Go to the set of double lights and turn right at the second light. Go through the next set of lights. Before the next set of double lights pass Chef Restaurant Supplies on the left corner. Go through both sets of lights. Take a few steps and stop just before the garden on the left.

Go to the fourth set of lights passing REI and Happy Paws along the way. Turn left at the fourth set of lights. Pass Hollister on the left corner. Stop at Victoria's Secret on the right and Harvest Works on the left.

Walk all the way to the end of the street and turn left. Go by a left side street and almost immediately after at an intersection with Noho Star on the far corner, turn right. Walk to the next light and turn right. Stop about 1/3 of the way down the block next to Dashwood Books on the right.

Go straight and take a right at the next light where Pink is on the left. Go through the next lightless intersection and at the next one with a light go straight. At the next light go right and stop one stop later.

Go through the first three traffic lights. You will pass a playground and Dominique Ansel Bakery on the right on the way to the 4th light. Turn right at the 4th light. Go to the end of the block and stop a few steps before the next intersection.

Go straight and you should see a double street intersection with two lights. Take a left at the first light. Go straight through 1 light and at the following light take a right. Stop adjacent to the corner building on the block, possibly near Miss Lily's restaurant and a mail drop off place.

Walk through one set of lights. There will be a second set of lights immediately after. Turn left. Walk down through two sets on lights on this road. At the third light, turn right. Walk down until almost the end of this block. Stop parallel to the top of the building on your left.
Go straight down the block and at the next light take a left. Go through the double light intersection and immediately take a right then stop.

Go straight to the light and turn left. Pass Petsmart on the left, Crate and Barrel on the right. Go through the two double lights. Keep going straight, passing Bank of America. Turn right at the next light. Stop a couple of steps before you get to the next light, just in front of the last building on the left - maybe Nespresso.

Head straight past the following 2 lights. At the 3rd light with Hollister on the near left corner, turn left. Go down the block to the next light with Victoria Secret on the far right corner. Cross the street, take a step, then stop in front of Converse, which is across the street from a bus stop.

Turn on right side street just after Olive Tree Cafe. Take left side street and follow the road past a green space on the right and to the lights where you will turn left. Pass the ball field on the left and at the first set of lights at the double light intersection turn right. Take a few steps and stop at green space on left.

Go to the light and turn right. Turn left at the side street after puck fair. Cross through the following intersection near Benetton. Turn right at the T-intersection. Now a library is on the right and a church on left. Continue past the churches and when you get to the light go through. Stop after a few steps.

Head to the first light and make a right. Pass the small park on the left and go past Duane Reade on the right. Go through the light and all the way down the block to the next light and make a left. Head to the next intersection at the end of the short block and stop there.

Head through the first light and at the second light make a right. Head all the way down the block and at the corner with Astor Wines make a right. Head up to the end of the first building and stop there.

Head to the light and turn left. Go past the 1st light with Starbucks on the right. At the 2nd light, you should see two streets to your right. Make a right onto the 2nd farther right with Duane Reade at the corner. Walk almost to the end of the block and stop just before reaching the light. The park should be on your right.

Walk to the large intersection with Whole Foods on the far right corner and turn right at the 1st light. Go by a couple of restaurant supply stores on the right passing a left side street until you reach an intersection where you can turn right. Go on it and stop a step before the next light by a mail box with Cafe Habana across.

Go straight to the intersection and make a left. Go straight through two lights. At the third light, make a left. Stop less than halfway to the first light, a step past La Newyorkina on your right and Sacred Chow on your left. Destination is VBar & Cafe on your left.

Turn left at the end of the block. Pass some alleys or small side streets directly across from each other, then turn right at the light. Go almost to the end of the block and stop just before The Bowery Hotel on the left.

Walk all the way down the block to the light and turn right. Go through a light with The Perfect Fit and SoHo Cafe on the corners and then another after it. At the following light with Isabel Marant on the far left corner, stop in the middle of the intersection.

Go to the lights and turn left. At the following set of lights, turn right. Go to the end of the block. Hollister will be on the right corner. Stop at the end of this building before reaching the intersection.

Head to the first light with Pink in the left corner and make a left. Continue through the next light where Mercer Kitchen is on the corner. Pass through one more light and at the following light with Cole Han on the far left, make a right. Stop in front of North Face on the left.

Go through the first light of the double intersection, and turn left at the second of the double intersection's lights. Hollister should now be on your right. Go to the light and turn right. Take the first possible left. Cross through the intersection with Benetton on the corner. At the T-intersection, turn right and stop.

Head straight through the next light you get to. At the following light, there may be a green space to your right. Turn left here. at the next light, turn right. Stop shortly after turning, just before Laduree on the right.

Head to the first light and make a right. Go past the next light passing a museum. You will pass an intersection on your right and at the next light with a Whole Foods on the right corner, turn right. Take a few steps and then stop in front of Whole Foods.

Turn right at the first set of lights. Go through a light and pass a playground on the right, do not take the right fork. Go through two more lights that are very close and pass a ballfield on the right and a right turn. At the following lights turn right and stop as the green space on the left ends.

Pass the bike rental on the right and then turn left. Google Store will be on your right after your turn. Go straight until you have passed a Starbucks on the right and subway entrances on either side of the street from each other after that. Turn left at the next corner and stop in front of Chloe on the left.

Turn right at the light ahead. Go straight through three more lights. You'll pass a bus stop, then Adidas, then Crate and Barrel on the right. Stop just before the next light, with Angelika Film Center on the near right corner.

Go through the light right in front of you. Pass REI on the left, and turn left at the light. Go through the following intersection with Benetton on the corner. At the following light, G-Star Raw will be on the corner, turn right. Go through the intersection with Juice Generation and stop 1/2 down block, near Dean and Deluca.

Go forward passing a museum on the left to double light intersection and turn right at the 1st one. Pass a bunch of small shops and through 2 lights where the Bowery Hotel is on the 2nd. Stop shortly after 1/2 to the next light next to Think Coffee on the right.

Walk to the corner and turn right. Walk to the light and turn left. The GMT Tavern will be on your right. You'll pass the gardens on your left. Go through the next two lights. Pass the Starbucks on the right and stop several steps past Dos Caminos on the left.

Move to the intersection and turn left. Head to the next intersection and make a right after passing the Turtle Conservancy. Go to the second intersection and turn left stopping right before the bicycle rental on the right.
Go to the lights and turn right. Go through the next 2 sets of lights. Miss Paradis will be on the left just before the next set of lights. Turn right here and stop.

Go to the first set of lights at the double lighted intersection and turn left where Happy Paws is on the near right corner. Go to the 4th light, turn right where Chef Restaurant Supplies is on the near left corner and stop in the intersection of the second light of the double lighted intersection.

Go straight to the intersection and turn left. Go straight through a double intersection with two lights. A baseball field is to your left after the lights. Go straight to the next light with By Chloe on the corner and turn right. Go straight through one light. At the next light turn left. Stop just after turn by The Red Lion.

Head up the first block passing the Noho Star on the left and go through the intersection. Go through the next light and at the following light make a left. Go just past the bike rental and then stop in front of Screaming Mimi's.
Go straight and take a left at the next intersection where Starbucks is. At the next intersection take a right and go past Tomoe Sushi and continue through the next intersection and stop at Toloache.

Go to the light, passing Dashwood Books, and turn left. Pass through two intersections, The Noho Star is on the corner of the second one. When you get to the following intersection, Happy Paws on the corner, it is a double light intersection. Go through the first of the lights, and stop in the intersection of the second one.

Go straight. Where the road branches, keep going straight. Pass by Petrosino Park. Go to the next intersection. Don't take the sharp immediate right turn. Instead take the turn ahead to the right, passing by Duane Reade. Turn left at the next intersection. Go until you reach one building past Grey Dog on the right.

Go straight past the first 3 lights. You should have passed Harney & Sons on your right. At the 4th light, turn left. Continue to the next light and stop in the intersection. You should see a small park on your far right.

Turn right at the light ahead, which is just after the bike rental. Go straight through one light and then straight through the next intersection, which has no light. At the next intersection, with The Noho Star on the corner, turn left. Take an immediate right at the next street. Bite will be on your right. Stop just after it.

Head through the first light and pass e.l.f. studio before going through another light. Go through two more lights and then with Aldo on the left corner make a left. Stop just past Aldo on the other side.

Go straight until you hit a stoplight. Turn right there, with The Dutch on the opposite corner. Go straight through another light, then turn left at the next one. When you make your left turn, you will come upon Casio G Shock on the left. Keep going until the third to last building on the left, which is two before Starbucks.

Go to the light with Apple Store on the corner and turn right. Go all the way to the light at the end of the block, passing Warby Parker. It will be a double intersection, turn left at the first light. At the next intersection, turn right. Turn left right away. Pass Pegu Club on the left, Landscape on the right, stop at light.

Starting at a set of light go to the next set and turn left and go through the lights immediately after. Chef Restaurant Supplies is on your left corner. Go through the next three sets of lights. Pass The Bowery Hotel on your left and stop at the bus station right after the hotel ends.

Head to the double lights ahead. Cross the street to the other side, then turn right. Walk to the next light with Hollister on the left corner, then turn left. Continue to the end of the block and stop one step before the following light. Prada should be on your right side.

Turn left at the first set of lights and right at the following lights. At the next set of lights with The Red Lion on the right turn left. Pass Quantum Leap on the right and stop at Go!Go! CURRY! on the left, close to the end of the block.

Walk to the light with Chanel on the far corner and turn right. Pass Diesel to the next light and turn left. Walk all the way to the next light with an Apple Store on the far right corner. Pass through it and stop about a 1/3 down the block next to Warby Parker on the left.

Turn right at the lights. Go through three sets of lights passing the NYU Philosophy Dept on the left as you do so. Turn left at the next set of lights with Duane Reade on the far right corner. Stop in the middle of the block, as the second building on the left starts. Blink Fitness is on the right.

Pass Hollister to the double light intersection and turn left at the 2nd. Pass a film center and 2 lights and at the following light, NYU campus buildings should be on the right. Stop in the intersection with the mailbox on the far right.

Go down the block when you hit a light with a triangular park on the right. Turn left and go through 2 lights, one with SoHo Anita Dongre on the corner and Isabel Marant on the other. Stop about 1/2 to the next light, before reaching Suit Supply on the right.

Go straight past the double set of lights just ahead of you with Arturo's Pizza on the left corner. Continue down the block to the next light, then make a left turn. Go past the next light with Happy Socks on the right corner. Go to the end of the next block and stop just before the last store on right, which is Cole Haan.

Go to the first intersection with double lights and turn right at the second light. Go through the following light with The Bowery Market on the left corner. Turn left at the following light with Crunch on the right far corner. Stop at the empty area before Merchant's House Museum on the right.

Head to the end of the block with Chanel on the corner and turn right. At the next light with SoHo Anita Dongre on the right corner, turn left. Go through the next light with Isabel Marant on the right corner. Go 2/3 block and stop in front of Suit Supply on right, which is the 2nd building from the next light.

Head to the end of the block and make a left with Chanel on the far right corner. Go through the next light and pass Boqueria on the right. Go through another light with a small playground on your right and stop just past that and before Dominique Bakery.

Begin heading down the street and take a slight left at the first intersection. Continue straight past the first two T-intersections on your right, then take a right at the third intersection with Duane Reade on the far right corner. End about 1/3 of the way down this block.

Go straight to the intersection and make a left. You'll immediately pass a street intersecting on your right. Proceed then to the next street intersecting on your right and turn right. Pass through the next double intersection with two lights. Stop two-thirds to the next light beside main building of Saint Patrick's Cathedral.

Turn right at the light ahead. Pass Cole Haan on the left before going through two stoplights. An intersection without a light will come before the stoplights. At the third light, turn right. Stop just before Once Upon a Tart on the right, in the second building.

Go straight to the traffic light and turn left. Go straight through 2 traffic lights and at the following light, there should be a Starbucks and MUJI at MoMA on the corners. Stop in the middle of this intersection.

Head straight through the next set of double lights with Arturo's Pizza on the left corner. Continue down the next block and turn right at the following light. Go almost all the way down the block and stop right when you reach the the last storefront on the right, which is The Dutch.

Go straight to the first intersection, take a left and continue past the first intersection, when you reach the 2nd intersection take a right, go straight and stop before you reach Pepe Rosso on your right.

Walk to the double light intersection and turn left and the 2nd one. Pass a bus stop and go through 2 lights and at the following light, 2 bus stop should be ahead on either side. Turn left and go through the entirety of the intersection. Stop in the intersection of a left side street, just before Housing Works Cafe.
Pass the bike rental on the left and then turn left. Go straight for two blocks and turn right after Longchamp on the right. Stop in front of Versus Versace on the right.

Pass the cemetery on the right and go through the first set of lights. At the following lights with Phebes on the right corner turn left and continue through the light immediately after. Go to the end of the block and turn right at Astor Wines & Spirits. Take a few steps past La Colombe on the left and stop.

Go past Casio to the light and turn left. Walk through an intersection with Cole Haan on the corner and then the following one as well with Apple Store on the far corner. At the next light you will cross it as well. Stop a couple steps before the next light next to Pink and Prada just before some subway entrances on each side.

Turn left at the second light. Pass Think Coffee on the right, then turn right. Turn left at the side street. Go straight through a double intersection before stopping at Tacombi on the right. Toms is on the left shortly before it.

Walk passing a rec center on the right to a light which has a film center on the corner and turn right. Walk to the next light, turn left then immediately turn right so you are parallel to the street you were just on. Go through an intersection and stop 1/2 to the light, next to Pegu Club and a bus stop on the left.

Go to the light with Mercer Kitchen on the corner and turn left. Walk through a light with Prada and Pink on the corners and past another intersection until a light with G-Star and Soho Park on the corners. Turn left and stop after a few steps, next to Supreme and La Colombe Coffee.

Go and turn right. Pass Charley Bird on the left, and turn left when you can no longer go straight. When you come to the double intersection with Harry's Corner Shop, go through the first light and turn right at the second of the two. Pass Miss Lily's on the left, and go through the light. Stop in the next intersection.

Immediately go straight through two lights in immediate succession. Continue through the next light, and then at the next light - where the street dead ends - turn right. Stop one step before the first light.

Turn right at the first set of lights. Pass Pink on the right and go through the lights. Pass Dean and Deluca on the right and go through another intersection. With G-Star Raw on the left corner, turn left at the next set of lights. Pass Scotch & Soda on the right and stop at Pravda new York on right, Supreme on left.

Walk down the block passing Casio Shock to the light and turn left. At the next intersection with Cole Haan on the right, turn right. Pass Rayban all the way to the next light with Chanel on the corner. Stop in the middle of the intersection.

Go through a light and at the following double intersection with a garden and restaurant supply store on the left corners, turn right. Go through the intersection and pass the Whole Foods. Walk forward until you reach a left side street. Stop 1 step after crossing it. A light should be close ahead. Bari Equipment may be nearby.

Walk to the light with Chanel on the far corner. Turn right and pass through 2 lights, the 2nd of which has Solstice and a Google Store on the corners. At the next light with Chase, turn left. Take an extra step and stop. Niketown should be on your left.

Walk through a light and go by a NYU building on the right. Ignore a left side street and when you reach the next intersection, turn right. Walk by Think Coffee to the next light and turn left. At the next light with Le Basket, turn right. Stop a few steps before the next light right next to a bus stop on the right.

Walk to the double light intersection and turn left at the 1st one. Go through the next 3 intersections, the second of which has no left turn and the 3rd has Angelika Film Center on the far corner. At the next light with Hollister on the far right corner, turn left. Stop after a couple steps next to Crate and Barrel and Adidas.
Walk to the corner with Chase Bank and turn left. Go past the 1st light with Prada on the left corner. Walk to the 2nd light with Hollister, then stop when you reach the light.
Continue through the 1st and 2nd intersections. At the 3rd take a right. Continue past the alley and the bike rental station and stop in the middle of the 1st intersection.

Turn left at the corner. Pass a bike rental on the right and then go straight until you have gone through a double intersection. Stop between Time Landscape on your right and Silver Spurs on your left. If you reach a garden on the right, you've gone too far.

Proceed ahead to the traffic lights. Here you have two sets of traffic lights back to back. Turn right at the 2nd set of lights. Go straight through the next three sets of traffic lights. At the next light you'll turn left. Go down the street until you have an available left turn and mark this as your destination.

Pass a left side street and turn right at the corner. Go through the next intersection with no lights and then through the following 3 sets of lights. Take about 4 steps and stop. Just after Astor Wines on the right corner and La Colombe on the left corner.

Make a left at the first light. Go past two subway entrances on opposite ends, then go through the next light with Starbucks on the left corner. Make a left at the next light with SoHo on the left corner. Go past H&M on the left and stop right before North Face on the right and Old Navy on the left.

Turn left at the light in front of you. Go straight through one light before turning right at the stoplight after that. There will be a playground on your right as you make your turn. Stop when you're halfway down the green space of the park.

Turn right immediately at the light in front of you. Go straight through one light, passing Le Poisson Rouge on the left. At the next light, turn left. There is The Half Pint on the right before your turn. Stop when you reach the second to last building on the left before the next light.

Walk straight to the double light intersection and turn right at the 2nd light. Walk to the next light and turn left. Go straight to the next light and turn right. Pass through another light and stop a few steps after crossing the intersection, next to the Mercer Kitchen on the right or the 2nd building of the block on the left.

Go to the traffic light and turn right. Continue straight through 1 light and at the following light turn left. Again go straight through the next light and stop just before the roads all merge into the next intersection. You should have just passed a mini square or plaza on the right. A bike rental should also be nearby.

Go straight through the first intersection. Continue straight through the next intersection. Pass a bus station on the right. Go straight through the next intersection by Angelika Film Center. At the next crossing by Hollister and Adidas turn right. Stop when you see Victoria's Secret on the right and Harvest Works on the left.

Go straight to intersection and turn right. At first intersection just after Shakespeare & Co. on right, turn left. Go straight through first two intersections and stop one step before the end of the next intersection where road ends. Washington Square Park is directly ahead.

Turn left at the stoplight ahead. At the next light, turn right. Then turn left immediately at the next light. Go straight through one more light before passing a ballfield on the right. Turn right at the stoplight after the ballfield and stop in front of the bus stop on the right. If you see a right side street, you're too far.

Begin going straight through a traffic light, passing a church on the right until you reach a double light intersection. Turn right at the second light and go straight but stop just before the next light, next to a bus stop on the left.

At the light ahead, with Apple Store, SoHo to your near left, turn right. Go straight through one 4-way intersection then two more stoplights, passing Cole Haan and Happy Socks on the left. Stop just before the next light, with Dutch on your near right corner.
