Turn left at the light that is directly in front of you. At the following light, with Prada on the corner, turn left. Go through the following intersection with Juice Generation on the corner. When you get to the light, G-Star on the corner, turn right. Pass a parking area on the right and stop in front of Ladder 20 Fire on left.

Take a left at the next light. Go through the T-intersection and at the next light where Pink is on the corner take a right. Go almost down the whole block and stop one stop before reaching the next light.

Head to the intersection and make a right. Go to the next intersection and make a left. You will go around the bend and pass a small park on the right. When you get to the light make a left. Head all the way down to the lights and make a right at the second immediate light and then stop.

Head straight around the bend to the T-intersection, then turn right. At the following T-intersection with Olive Tree Cafe on left, turn left. Go to the next light with Ben's Pizza and turn right. Go past the following light. At the next light with The Half Pint on the right corner, turn right, take one step and stop.
At the light right in front of you, make a right turn. Proceed to the 4th light with Whole Foods and a garden on the left corners, turn right, then stop.

Head to the first light and continue through it. At the next light you will make a right. You will pass a Duane Reade on your left and you will come to another light with Taim on the corner. Make a left here and head all the way down almost to the light and stop at McNally Jackson on left.

Head straight to the end of the block and turn right. At the next light, turn left. NYU business school should be on your left. Continue through the next 2 intersections. Stop about 1/4 of the way down the block in front of the 1st building which is the NYU Philosophy Department.

Go to the traffic light and turn the left. Go through the next light and turn to the right at the second light after passing a Duane Reade on the left. Go all the way to the end of the block, stopping before reaching the light, after the parking area on the left and about 1/2 way to the end of the last building on the left.

Turn left at the light. Go through the next light, then pass Sunrise Mart on the right. Turn right at the next light. Go almost to the end of the block and stop. This will be right after passing Laduree on the left.

Go straight and turn right at the next intersection. Go past the next T-intersection that opens to the right. At the next light with Think Coffee on the left corner, turn left. Turn left at the next intersection. Take one step and stop. Brookdale Center should be on your left.

Turn right at the lights. Pass school buildings on your right and go through the first intersection. Pass Duane Reade on the right and turn left at the lights. Head towards the next lights passing Aldo, Le Chateau and then American Apparel. Shortly before the lights you will stop at Shakespeare & Co.

Head straight to the first light and make a right. You will pass by an intersection and another light with Soho Park restaurant on your right. You will stop at the next light with McNally Jackson on your right and Miss Paradis on your left.

Head to the light and turn left. At the next light with The Red Lion on the right corner, turn right. Turn left at the next light with a garden on the right corner. Go almost to the end of the block and stop one step before reaching the next light.

Go straight and turn right at the second set of lights you come to. Take your first left. Cross through the intersection. Look for Toms on your left and Tacombi on your right, this is where you want to stop.

Go straight until you pass a bike rental on the right. Then turn right after REI on the right. Pass a bus stop and cross the street. Stop after a small courtyard on the right. You may be able to see a bus stop on your left. If you reach another light, you've gone too far.

Pass a school to get to a 4-way intersection and turn left. Walk past a side street and a 4-way intersection until you reach a light with KITH and Nom de Guerre on the corners. Turn left and stop 1/2 to the next light, next to CEX, Roni and Mariatash on the left. Starbucks is slightly too far.

Take a left at the next light and then a right at the one after that where Ben's Pizzeria is. Go through the next 2 lights and at the 3rd one after them stop just before you hit the middle of the intersection, a bike rental will be on the right.

Head through the first light and pass rapha cycling on the right. Go through another light and at the next corner will be the Dutch. Go through one more light and then make a right. Pass Rouge et Blanc on the right and stop in front of 12 Chairs on the right.

Continue straight to the first light and then make a right. Take that to the end of the block and make a right at Astor Wines and Spirits. Head down the block until there is a parking area on the left and Colors restaurant on your right.

Go to first set of lights, turn right. There will be another set very close, turn left. At the next set of lights turn right. Go down a block and take the first left available. Go to end of the block. Benetton should be on the left corner. Cross the intersection and go to the end of the block. Stop just before the intersection.

There is a garden to your left. Turn right after you pass it. Go straight through two lights, the first of which is immediately after your turn. Turn left at the next one and go straight immediately through the next. Stop after the first cemetery on your right, at the front edge of the cathedral.

At the first corner with Crunch on the left, turn right at the lights. Go through the next two sets of lights passing Bowery Market and Bowery Hotel on the right corners. Pass Think Coffee on the right and go to the lights and stop.

Go to the lights with Our Lady of Pompei Church on the corner and turn right. Go through the next set of lights. Do not turn, the street will angle, but you will not make a turn. Go 2 blocks and pass through the light. Go to the 3rd building on your left hand side. It should be just before Uncle Ted's.

Go forward and take your first right. Take your next left, Olive Tree Cafe will be on this corner. Turn right at the lights. Go through the next set of lights and follow the next block to the end. You will pass Legend West Village and Amity Hall on your right. Stop when you are almost in to the intersection.

Pass the library on the right, and go through the light. At the next intersection, turn right. You'll pass Think Coffee on the left and when you get to the light, turn left. At the following light, Le Basket on the corner, turn right and stop after a couple steps.

Make a quick left at the intersection just ahead with bike rentals on the left corner. Go straight past the next set of traffic lights with Angelika Film Center on the left. Continue to the next traffic light with Fanelli Cafe on the right corner, then turn right. Stop at the next traffic light with Apple Store on right corner.

Go to the light directly in front and turn right. Go straight until a left side street and take that one until you can't go straight anymore. Saint Michael's Church should be in front of you. Turn right and go to the next light, passing another church on the left. Cross the intersection and stop on the other side, near McNally.

Go straight to the light and turn right. Pass two streets intersecting only on your left. At the third street intersecting on your left, turn left. Go straight to the first light and then cross the median and pass the second light immediately after the first. Stop right after the intersection by The Market NYC on your left.

Take a left at the intersection ahead. At the next intersection by Chef Restaurant Supplies, turn right in the first lane. Go straight across the secondary lane, passing by Whole Foods Market. Continue straight until the road offers a left turn just past the ICP museum on your right by Bari Pizza. Stop before taking the turn.

Head straight and go through the double set of lights with the post office on the far right corner. Go to the following light and turn right. Go past the 1st light with the Red Lion on the left corner. At the 2nd light with a small garden on the far right corner, turn right and stop immediately.

Go to the light and take a left where the bus stop is. Go straight through the next light less intersection and the lighted intersection after that. At the following light take a left where the film center is and stop in front if it.

Turn right at the first stoplight ahead, with The Bowery Hotel on the left. Turn right again at the next stoplight, with Think Coffee on the right. Pass one street on the left before turning left down the next street. Go to the center of the next stoplight intersection and stop.
Go straight through the intersection and 2 close lights. Go through the next light as well past the park on the left. At the next light take a right and stop at Loreley beer garden.

Head to the intersection with bike rentals on the far right corner and turn right. Go past the next 3 intersections with GMT Tavern on the far left corner. Stop at the 4th light with The Red Lion on the near right corner.

Go straight through the first three lights, including one almost immediately after starting. At the fourth light make a left. Go straight to the first intersection and make a left again. The street will dead end at Saint Michael's Church. Make a right there and stop after a step or two with the church grounds to your left.

Go to the light where Happy Socks is on the near right corner and turn left. Go down the block and after the Starbucks on the left go through two traffic lights, one immediately after the other. Continue to the next intersection passing LaGuardia Corner Gardens on the right and stop under the light.

Walk to the corner with Duane Reade and turn right. Walk a couple blocks to La Colombe to the double light intersection. It has BBar & Grill and Phebes on the right corners. Turn right at the 1st light and stop after a few steps just where the Phebes building ends.

Pass a bus stop and Chipotle to reach a double light intersection. Go through it and pass Bank of America and Under Armour to reach the next light. A bunch of subway entrances are on the corners. Turn left and stop 1/2 down the block, a couple steps after passing the subway entrances. You may be next to Dean and Deluca.

Go to the light and take a right then a left at the light after that. Go past the clothing shop on the left and take a right at the next light where the coffee shops are. Stop under the next light where the bike rental is.

Walk by a Vans to the light and turn left. Go by Fiorentini on the right to the next light and turn right. At the next light with SoHo Cafe and a mail box on the near left corner, turn left. Stop about 3/4 down the block next to H&M on the left before a bus stop. You should have just passed Old Navy.

Head to the end of the block and make a left at the light. Go through the light and at the next intersection you will make a right. Head half way down the block and go just past the Creperie on the right and then stop.

Go past the Adidas on the left through the double intersection. Pass Hollister and an Under Armour store on the way to the next light. Pink is on the corner. Turn left and walk 2 blocks to the light with G-Star and Scotch & Soda on the corners. Turn left and stop 1 step after turning.

Head straight past the double set of lights with Starbucks on the right corner. At the following light with Happy Socks on the far right corner, turn left. Go past the next intersection with Cole Haan on right. Continue to the next light with Apple Store SOHO on the left corner and stop in the intersection.

Walk to the end of the road and turn right. You'll go through 4-way intersection near The Noho Star and Bite and two right side streets. At the following right side street, turn and walk to the light. Turn left and stop a step before the next light, with a restaurant supply store on the left and a garden on the far left corner.

Go to the light with an Apple Store on the corner and turn left. You'll pass through 4 intersections until you reach a light with a large church on the far left corner. Don't enter it through, stop a step before reaching the intersection next to McNally Jackson and Miss Paradis.

Walk to the corner and turn left. Walk one block until you reach the light and turn right. You've now got a park on your left. Walk one block to the light and turn left. You will still have the park on your left. Walk past a right turn only. Before you get to the first light, you'll see a bike rental. Stop just past it.

Go straight to the traffic light and turn right. Go to the next intersection where by Chloe is on the corner. Turn left and go all the way to the light. A park should be on the right. Turn right and stop just before the road starts forking. The park or field should still be on your right.

Go down the block and turn left at the light. Walk through the light with Happy Socks on the corner and the next light with Cole Haan on the right. Cross the next light with an Apple store on the far corner. Pass the Mercer Kitchen to the next light and cross it. Stop a couple steps after crossing before subway entrances ahead.

Go to the first light, passing a playground on the right, and turn left. Go through two intersections, passing Balthazar on your left after the second and then turn right at the third. Stop immediately with the Nike store to your left.

Go through the first traffic light and follow to the next double intersection. Go through the first light and at the next light immediately following turn to the left. Follow down the block and stop just before reaching the traffic light, just at the corner of the last building on the right should contain a Pizza place and bar.

Go to the light and turn left. Go by Adidas and through 2 lights, the 2nd of which has Chase and Niketown on the near corners. At the next light with Starbucks on the far corner, stop in the middle of that intersection.

Head through the first intersection and pass a Starbucks on your left before going through the next light. Make a right at the next light with a Le Basket on your left. Head through the intersection and before coming to the next light stop with a bike rental on your left.

Turn left at the end of the block. Pass the mail drop on the left before going straight through two lights in quick succession. Keep going and pass St. Anthony of Padua Church on the left. Keep going several more steps until you reach Once Upon a Tart on the left. Stop just before it.
Turn left at the light and go through another one immediately. Pass the fire station and parking lot on the right, then turn right. Stop just before Screaming Mimi's on the left.

Head straight through the first two intersections and when it Ts at the third make a left. At the next intersection you will make a right and head to the next light to make a left. You will stop half way up the block before the next light with Mercer Residence hall on your right.

Head through the first intersection and you will go through the next light. You will then pass rapha cycling on the right. Go through the next light and at the following light with the Dutch on the right make a left. Head 3/4 of the way down the block and stop just pass the playground on left.

Turn left at the corner. Keep going straight to pass a very long garden on the left. Turn right at the light afterwards. Go straight through the immediate intersection. Pass Subway on the right, take a step, then stop. There will be a park on your left.

Go straight to the light and turn right. Go straight through the first intersection without a light and the second intersection with a light. At the next light make a left. Go straight with Saint Patrick's Cathedral on your right. Stop two steps before a street intersects on your left, before Mulberry Branch on the left.

Go straight through three lights passing Apple Store, The Mercer Kitchen, and Dean and Deluca. Go through the intersection after Dean and Deluca and turn left at the stoplight with G-Star Raw and Soho Park on the corners. Stop in front of La Colombe on the left and Scotch Soda on the right.

Starting in an intersection, go to the next corner and turn right. At the lights, turn left. At the following set of lights turn right and you will immediately be at another set of lights where you will turn left. At the end of the street, turn right at the lights. You will be beside Angelika Film Center. Stop here.
